documentation.text:
@dev Atomically decreases the allowance granted to `spender` by the caller.
 This is an alternative to {approve} that can be used as a mitigation for
 problems described in {IERC20-approve}.
 Emits an {Approval} event indicating the updated allowance.
 Requirements:
 - `spender` cannot be the zero address.
 - `spender` must have allowance for the caller of at least
 `subtractedValue`.

This is an alternative to {approve} that can be used as a mitigation for problems described in {IERC20-approve}. Emits an {Approval} event indicating the updated allowance. Requirements: - `spender` cannot be the zero address. - `spender` must have allowance for the caller of at least `subtractedValue`.
